    "epitet": "Shadow Prince",
    "description": "Prince of Grado; not fond of fighting. A childhood friend of Ephraim and Eirika. Appears in Fire Emblem: The Sacred Stones.",
    "artist": "Miyajima Haru (ミヤジマハル)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Mark P. Whitten",
    "voiceActorJP": "中村悠一",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "It is good to meet you. I am Lyon, prince of Grado. I hope that we can become friends.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "Ephraim is strong, and he cuts a dashing figure. When it comes to his studies, though... Of course, he did rely on my help for that. I was very glad to aid him.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "My kingdom, Grado, can be a harsh and inhospitable place. Still, I do love my homeland.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You work so hard, but I want you to know that—if you need to—it's OK to cry. Nobody here knows what you've been through but you.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I am useless with a sword. Eirika disarms me so quickly... It's really an embarrassment.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I tripped just a moment ago. My leg still hurts, but it hasn't ruined my mood in the slightest. It's strange. Being alive is wonderful, isn't it?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I am Lyon. I am glad to meet you, <Player Name>. May my visit sustain your friendship with <Friend Name>.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "Something rises from deep within me. With this, I can be of aid...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I think I've progressed a little. Yes, I'm certain of it.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I cannot remain despondent... I will redeem myself.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "No books have taught me of power like this. I'm glad of this strength, but...a little scared.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "To tell the truth...some of my memories from before I came to this world...are lost. It's all so indistinct, as though a fog has been cast on them. And other things, I can't remember at all... I feel like I may have done some things that would make the people dear to me so very sad. Oh, <Player Name>... You are far too kind. Please don't look at me so. I want to see you smile. Always. I had friends back home who worried about me just as you do... Dear friends. Ephraim, Eirika... I hope that someday, we can gather together for a good, long chat.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
